item.title: Harvard CS50
item.description: going to Harvard at night. I’ve been studying computer science since last week and while I was looking for some stuff I found great foundation lectures on CS at Harvard.In fact I was able to watch the whole lectures throughout the weekend and It was really helpful for someone like me(no background in computer science). 하버드에 가지않고 하버드에 다녀오
